<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <!-- <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> -->
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">

  <title>Document</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Questrial&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/normalize.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <%- include('modules/nav'); %>
    <main id="main">
      <header id="header">
        <h1 class="header__title">咬一口廚房 </h1>
      </header>
      
      <section class="menu block">
        <h2 class="block__title">
          <span>
            Menu 搶先看
          </span>
        </h2>
        <div class="menu__gallery">
          <figure><img src="./images/home/f-001.png" 
                       alt="黯然消魂飯" 
                       srcset="./images/home/f-001@2x.png 2x,
                               ./images/home/f-001@3x.png 3x"></figure>
          <figure><img src="./images/home/f-002.png" 
                       alt="海景佛跳牆" 
                       srcset="./images/home/f-002@2x.png 2x,
                               ./images/home/f-002@3x.png 3x"></figure>
          <figure><img src="./images/home/f-003.png" 
                       alt="爆漿瀨尿牛丸" 
                       srcset="./images/home/f-003@2x.png 2x,
                               ./images/home/f-003@3x.png 3x"></figure>
          <figure><img src="./images/home/f-004.png" 
                       alt="雜碎麵" 
                       srcset="./images/home/f-004@2x.png 2x,
                               ./images/home/f-004@3x.png 3x"></figure>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="reviews block">
        <h2 class="block__title">
          <span>
            吃過都說好
          </span>
        </h2>
        <div class="reviews__board">
          <div class="reviews-block">
            <div class="reviews-block__avatar">
              <img src="./images/home/p-1.png" alt="國父桑" srcset="./images/home/p-1@2x.png 2x,
              ./images/home/p-1@3x.png 3x">
              <p>國父桑</p>
            </div>
            <p class="reviews-block__comment block__content">
              我一生疲於建國，去過日本，去過歐洲，卻從未到過台北101，也從來沒有吃過這麼好吃的東西...今天在時空旅行者的幫助下我終於吃到了...此生再無遺憾 QAQ!!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="reviews-block">
            <div class="reviews-block__avatar">
              <img src="./images/home/p-2.png" alt="可達鴨" srcset="./images/home/p-2@2x.png 2x,
              ./images/home/p-2@3x.png 3x">
              <p>可達鴨</p>
            </div>
            <p class="reviews-block__comment block__content">
              三雙鞋等於30，兩個人加一雙鞋等於20，一雙冰淇淋加一雙冰淇淋加一個人等於13，那$#%$#%^%$^##$%等於多少...唉，大概咬一口就知道了!!!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="reviews-block">
            <div class="reviews-block__avatar">
              <img src="./images/home/p-3.png" alt="旅かえる旅行青蛙" srcset="./images/home/p-3@2x.png 2x,
              ./images/home/p-3@3x.png 3x">
              <p>旅かえる旅行青蛙</p>
            </div>
            <p class="reviews-block__comment block__content">
              自從呱呱呱呱呱以後，我呱呱呱呱呱，非常感謝呱呱呱呱呱，下次呱呱呱呱呱我呱呱呱呱呱，一定呱呱呱呱呱!!!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>
      <section class="map block">
        <h2 class="block__title">
          <span>
            我們在哪裡
          </span>
        </h2>
        <div class="map__content">
          <iframe width="100%" height="100%" frameborder="0" style="border:0" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed/v1/place?key=AIzaSyC3VZAZvAVatXzUo3s5YOEAi3Wkr-dn50I&q=No.+7,+Section+5,+Xinyi+Rd,+Xinyi+District,+Taipei+City,+110" >
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('modules/footer'); %>
  </div>
</body>

</html>